Hi guys please could someone tell me how do work the keygen? It says refer to some text file which doesn't exist. Help Pleeeeeeeezzz!!! my little sister formatted my hd by mistake and i have important files i need to recover, any help will be hugely appreciated!!

Thanks seeders! :)
Easy, just click the Generate button, double-click the serial to copy it and paste into DR's reg. with name Keymaker.
BTW Disk Drill is also vg. So if DR does not get back what you want, try an alternative.

At least Disk Drill can recover files from your user account on the system drive, Data Rescue cannot. So much for having a user account work space on the system drive. I rarely use it but ... on this rare occasion and now ...

What an absolute legend. Man i can't tell you how grateful i am. I have had this harddrive sitting here for about 7 months. Tried downloading programs none worked - forget trying to buy software that may or maynot work.
Great big shout out.
Cheers brother.
